## 📋 dependency check commands

| package manager | audit command | outdated command | license command |
|-----------------|---------------|------------------|-----------------|
| **npm** | `npm audit` | `npm outdated` | `npm-license-crawler` |
| **yarn** | `yarn audit` | `yarn outdated` | `yarn licenses list` |
| **pip** | `pip-audit` | `pip list --outdated` | `pip-licenses` |
| **maven** | `mvn dependency-check:check` | `mvn versions:display-dependency-updates` | `mvn license:check` |
| **gradle** | `gradle dependencycheckanalyze` | `gradle dependencyupdates` | `gradle license` |

